==English==

===Adjective===
'''dehiscent'''

# {{medicine}} Of or pertaining to [[dehiscence]], i.e., a [[rupture]], as with a surgical wound opening up, often with a flow of [[serous]] fluid.
# {{botany}} Of or pertaining to the rupture of the reproductive organs in plants, leading to their diffusion in the air or deposition on the ground.

